data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! (ALL OFFERS WELCOME). $5000 Credit to Buyer's closing cost w/ Full price offer. Greenwater Dr is a hidden Oasis that is known and enjoyed by a few families "Everyone Buys Here, No One Sells". Inside the security gates you will find flat usable land with old growth trees. The house is placed about a 5 min walk to the Cowlitz River. You can fish for Chinook Salmon, Steelhead, Trout and the list goes on. The design of the house allows for expansion opportunity above the garage. Garage is 24X36 W/ 20 Ft Ceilings and 14-18 Ft Automatic doors. Updates include:New Water Heater, Flooring, Water filtration system and much more. Rent this home out as a Air BNB (Buyer to Verify) or just enjoy this Fisherman's Paradise year round.
